Step 1: Clone a repository
Step 2: Creating a virtual environment
    to create VE: python3 -m venv .venv -- in new terminal
Step 3: Activate virtual environment 
    to activate VE: source .venv/bin/activate
Step 4: Installing 3rd party library 
    pip3 install matplotlib

to ignore excess files type virtual environment name (.venv/) in 
.gitignore

_____________________

Non-green means that it is in your git repository, if green then
it is the current file you are owrking and the changes you have made. 

